OpenVZ executor for Sloth CI app extension that replaces the default executor and runs actions inside a given OpenVZ container.

Config params::

    [openvz_exec]
    ;Container name.
    container_name = foo
    ;Container ID.
    container_id = 123

If name is provided, ID is ignored. If name is not provided, ID is mandatory.


